title_bed_bats_review: Bed and breakfast in Dhaka · ★New · 3 bedrooms · 3 baths
listing_description:
Situated in Dhaka, 1.6 km from Daffodil International University, Dhaka features accommodation with a fitness centre, free private parking, a terrace and a restaurant. This 3-star hotel offers an ATM and a concierge service. The accommodation offers a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, room service and free WiFi throughout the property.

The rooms are fitted with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a minibar, a kettle, a bidet, free toiletries and a desk.
